data.enText: the leaves of a tree or plant; leaves and branches together

simple_means.memory_skill: foli 树叶 + age 集合名词，总称 → 树叶

tr: the main organ of photosynthesis and transpiration in higher plants

value.def: The leaves of a plant are referred to as its foliage .

example.tran: 长着灰色或银色叶子的灌木丛

foli 树叶 + age 集合名词，总称 → 树叶

use 使用 + age 行为或行为的结果 → 使用；惯用法
